Y9D61SRDiTAYJeaVbqvbFg
Was looking for BBQ chicken and ribs. This place came up so I took my my wife and kids there. The service was good but the food wasn't up to par... Ordered the BBQ chicken and it was flavorful but really tough and NOT tender at all! My wife ordered the ribs for her and the kids. The sauce is more spicy than I believe most kids can handle (8-12ys) and the rub they use on the rib is spicer than most would care to consume. The waitress was unsympathetic and handed me the bill... I wouldn't recommend this place to anyone that was interested in a decent BBQ experience. Pretty much a fancy bar. Lots of TV's for sports. Food an after thought...

